    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Structures, often tower-like, from which signals are sent to control the movements of railway trains. They typically house the control equipment for signal apparatuses and switches.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
